                 shows just how much better the competitors were this time. Having looked at the finishers and comparing to Ashridge on the 6th January the fastest time for my age category (30-34) went from a 02:48:23 (me, on the 6th Jan) to a 02:05:42 and the average went from a 03:08:48 to a 02:28:46 (so I wasn`t even near that) . I also noticed that within the top 10, 6 came from my category and of the top 20, 8 were in my group.</p>
